oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Eiffel Tower Model
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: Cultural relations; Festivals; Construction; Structures; Models
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Engineering students built this replica of the Eiffel Tower on Christian Brothers University campus. CBU celebrated "France with the Brothers" in conjunction with Memphis in May's 1990 tribute to France.
